{"tid":1950502,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[eTV] 明仔與家人聚餐","createTime":"2020-03-30T11:13:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T11:55:06.000Z","uid":86383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7e5c46bd15541b6dccd4dfc2d445e6e4ace9d4d7","tid":1950502,"uid":86383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T11:13:25.000Z","msg":"頭盔：<br />\n以下為設計劇情，如有雷同，實屬巧合<br />\n<br />\n老豆：阿仔，聽講英國爆得好勁喎！不如你都係返嚟避下啦！一家人最緊要齊齊整整！<br />\n<br />\n阿仔：好啦！咁我去撲下啲貴機票啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(接機嗰日)<br />\n<br />\n老豆：仔呀！難得返到香港，今晚約埋阿叔同你堂妹一齊食飯洗塵！...咳咳咳<br />\n<br />\n阿仔：嘩！老豆你有兩聲咳喎！<br />\n<br />\n老豆：開心得滯，口水俗親啫，唔驚唔驚<br />\n<br />\n(到食飯嗰時)<br />\n<br />\n侍應：呀先生！唔好意思，而家政府規定咗，一枱唔可以多過四個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n老豆：你家陣係咪有生意都唔撚做呀？我個仔喺外國返嚟咁撚鳩慶嘅日子，你掃鳩我慶？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n經理：er er er，好好 好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你哋隔開啲坐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n教育電視主持：<br />\n小朋友，我哋而家一齊數下<br />\n明仔同佢屋企人聚餐<br />\n究竟會有機會將傳染病感染俾幾多人呢？<br />\n計好答案就寫喺工作紙上面啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>eTV </strong></span><br />\nMMXX</div>"},{"pid":"bd1b3c6b510975271231846e6c3e03badabb68d6","tid":1950502,"uid":277137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T11:15:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"da6ae351dd7767d1dd7ca4b43d908184674d204c","tid":1950502,"uid":86383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd1b3c6b510975271231846e6c3e03badabb68d6","tid":1950502,"uid":277137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T11:15:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T11:20:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 